{"word":"σιναμωρέω","slug":"σιναμωρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σιναμωρέω</b></el> <el>(σῐνᾰμωρέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σινάμωρος'><el>σινάμωρος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to ravage</i> or <i>destroy wantonly</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be treated wantonly</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}